OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FEnergy firms remotely swap 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fhomes to prepay meters     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A rising number of households are      
OL,6, having their energy smart meters       
OL,7, remotely switched to prepayment meters,
OL,8, the energy regulator has said.         
OL,10,FSuppliers can use the technology to    
OL,11,Fswap customers onto a payment method   
OL,12,Fthat is often more expensive without   
OL,13,Ftheir permission.                      
OL,15,FIt can leave customers, who need to top
OL,16,Fup, at risk of running out of energy.  
OL,18,FOfgem said some had been left without  
OL,19,Fpower for days or even weeks, and a    
OL,20,Ftrade body said "mistakes" were made.  
